# Environment Maps Directory

Place HDRI environment maps here:
- skybox.hdr
- studio.hdr
- outdoor.hdr
- indoor.hdr

Recommended:
- 2K resolution for mobile
- 4K for desktop
- Pre-filtered for IBL (Image Based Lighting)

Tools:
- Poly Haven: https://polyhaven.com/hdris
- HDRI Haven (archived)
- Generate with Blender
